name: COMMONWEALTH of Pennsylvania, Appellant, v. Charles F. WUENSTEL, Jr., Appellee

parties: COMMONWEALTH of Pennsylvania, Appellant, v. Charles F. WUENSTEL, Jr., Appellee.

opinions.text:
ORDER
PER CURIAM.
AND NOW, this 23rd day of August, 2005, the Joint Motion to Remand Case to Common Pleas Level or for Alternative Relief is granted. This matter is remanded for reconsideration in light of the decision in Commonwealth v. Ludwig, 874 A.2d 623 (Pa.2005).
opinions.author: PER CURIAM.
